month to make enough repairs to the power plants to supply the city 
with three hours of electricity a day a municipal official said 
the syrians who have 40000 soldiers in lebanon provide 80 
tank trucks to carry water from the south 
the bloodletting between aoun and geagea is seen by many as the 
ultimate madness in a country thought to have seen it all 
