the april 8 election in the northern republic was the first free 
multiparty vote in yugoslavia since the communists took power in 
1945 
the official results showed that the demos coalition consisting 
of six centerright parties received 55 percent of the vote for 
places in the republics 140seat parliament 
the slovenian communist party which has ruled the republic 
