carbon dioxide which is produced in the burning of fossil 
fuels is responsible for about half the greenhouse pollutants 
environmentalists have argued that a wide range of actions could 
be taken to conserve energy and reduce greenhouse pollutants by 
requiring the manufacture of more fuelefficient cars and promoting 
energy savings in other ways in homes and businesses 
the sierra club which has more than 500000 members will take 
