arrests there in january they were returned to painesville on 
friday 
also monday two cult members were freed from the lake county 
jail after their charges were reduced 
dennis and tonya patrick each had been charged with five counts 
of conspiracy to commit aggravated murder each posted 10 percent 
of a 25000 bond on one count of complicity in attempted 
aggravated murder 
