nbc thus far had a 146 ratings average abc a 129 and cbs a 122 
during the season 
nbcs ratings are down by nine percent abcs are flat and 
those of cbs are down by three percent he said he cited 
competition from cable the fledgling fox network and independent 
stations as factors in the overall ratings drop 
however he attributed 25 percent of nbcs decline to the 
absence of three sports events it had in prime time during the 
previous season the summer olypmics the world series and pro 
footballs superbowl 
