in prison if convicted of all eight charges against him 
thompson is the author of several books written in a style that 
has come to be known as gonzo journalism intermingling a 
description of real events with exaggerated accounts of his own 
involvement which often include drug and alcohol abuse 
thompson ran a fullpage advertisement april 9 in the aspen 
times daily that read beware today the doctor tomorrow 
you the ad was paid for by the hunter s thompson legal 
