negotiations to sell 7 days were revealed last month but no 
qualified buyer came forward according to the principals 
the 7 days staff very quickly created a stylish provocative 
and useful publication said owner leonard stern but magazine 
startups are always a risky business and im deeply saddened that 
we couldnt generate the kind of advertising support that their 
professional efforts deserved 
